title: Unit 4: Fractions
text:
🔢 Module 13: Understand Fractions as Numbers


Explore how fractions represent parts of a whole and learn to place them on a number line.

Start Module 13



📐 Module 14: Relate Shapes, Fractions, and Area


Connect geometry and fractions by partitioning shapes and relating them to areas.

Start Module 14



📊 Module 15: Compare Fractions


Learn to compare fractions using models, number lines, and common denominators.

Start Module 15



➗ Module 16: Understand Equivalent Fractions


Develop a deep understanding of equivalent fractions and how to create and recognize them.

Start Module 16
